{"tid":1941314,"cid":12,"subCid":0,"title":"就快64，唔通郭文貴講中咗？","createTime":"2020-03-24T10:46:36.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-24T13:58:05.000Z","uid":345989,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"ebbe52310e36c1d0ede7b71e0011c23a4000c53f","tid":1941314,"uid":345989,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-24T10:46:36.000Z","msg":"仲有幾個月就64<br />\n<br />\n今年應該是中共最緊張嘅一年<br />\n<br />\n外交上開始比美國針對<br />\n<br />\n內部有疫症，民不聊生<br />\n<br />\n黨內部都開始有聲音反習近平<br />\n<br />\n最近聽講係中國啲網上面想upload片<br />\n<br />\n要審核幾個鐘先比你上<br />\n<br />\n可見佢哋有幾緊張<br />\n<br />\n上年64前連刀都唔比買<br />\n<br />\n睇怕今年連屋企門口都出唔到<br />\n<br />\n唔通真係俾郭文貴講中<br />\n<br />\n今年是中國最後一年64？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">歡迎公開討論</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">利申：想睇佢係18樓跳落去</span></span>"},{"pid":"d38b88b6974c1822f7dce206e84ccc80b4bca399","tid":1941314,"uid":263261,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-03-24T10:47:12.000Z","msg":"你太睇得起支那人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4bd7299ae0109830ff8f1b4e79963ed8fbc90f54","tid":1941314,"uid":34154,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"d38b88b6974c1822f7dce206e84ccc80b4bca399","tid":1941314,"uid":263261,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-03-24T10:47:12.000Z","msg":"你太睇得起支那人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-24T10:47:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces